'''紐約和紐澤西港'''（{{lang-en|Port of New York and New Jersey}}）是位於[[美國|美國]][[紐約都會區|紐約都會區]]的一座港口，[[紐約港|紐約港]]亦包含其中，歸[[紐約與紐澤西港務局|紐約與紐澤西港務局]]管理。紐約和紐澤西港是世界最大的天然港之一<ref name="nysm_wwii">[http://www.nysm.nysed.gov/research_collections/research/history/hisportofnewyork.html "Port in a Storm: The Port of New York in World War II"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nysm.nysed.gov/research_collections/research/history/hisportofnewyork.html |date=20140429044423 }}, Joseph F. Meany Jr. ''& al.'', NY State Museum, 1992-1998.</ref>，也是美國第三繁忙和美國東海岸最繁忙的港口<ref>{{Citation | last = American Association of Port Authorities | title = Port Industry Statistics | year = 2008 | url = http://www.aapa-ports.org/Industry/content.cfm?ItemNumber=900&navItemNumber=551 | accessdate = 2010-05-01 | archive-date = 2010-01-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100107091819/http://www.aapa-ports.org/files/Statistics/2004_US_PORT_CARGO_TONNAGE_RANKINGS.xls | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/22/nyregion/22port.html | work=The New York Times | first=Eric | last=Lipton | title=New York Port Hums Again, With Asian Trade | date=2004-11-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Finnegan |first=William |url=http://www.newyorker.com/archive/2006/06/19/060619fa_fact_finnegan |title=A Reporter at Large: Watching the Waterfront |publisher=The New Yorker |accessdate=2012-08-03}}</ref>，僅次於[[洛杉磯港|洛杉磯港]]和[[長堤港|長堤港]]。紐約和紐澤西港內還有多個自由貿易區<ref>{{cite web   | title = U.S. Foreign-Trade Zones   | work = Import Administration   | publisher = International Trade Administration   | date = January 13, 2013   | url = http://ia.ita.doc.gov/ftzpage/letters/ftzlist-map.html   | doi =    | accessdate = 2013-01-20   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160113084141/http://ia.ita.doc.gov/ftzpage/letters/ftzlist-map.html   | archive-date = 2016-01-13   | dead-url = yes   }}</ref><ref>{{Citation   | last = Tiefenbrun   | first = Susan    | title = Tax Free Trade Zones Of The World And In The United States   | publisher = Edward Elgar Publishing   | year = 2012   | url = http://books.google.nl/books?id=Bdz5eG3b2nwC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Tax+Free+Trade+Zones+Of+The+World+And+In+The+United+States&hl=en&sa=X&ei=f2r9UJTHFoqq0AXKyYHYDA&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=Tax%20Free%20Trade%20Zones%20Of%20The%20World%20And%20In%20The%20United%20States&f=false   | isbn = 978 1 84980 243 7   | quote = }}</ref><ref>{{cite web   | title = Foreign-Trade Zone 49   | publisher = PANYNJ   | url = http://www.panynj.gov/port/ftz-49.html   | accessdate = 2013-01-20}}</ref>。

